{"tid":2076243,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"撞名BLACK PINK成員　韓模Jisoo爆乳吸睛","createTime":"2020-06-23T11:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T12:11:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a55fa4c3db8ff5ddf610b34d3ef64ae691df32","tid":2076243,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:09:31.000Z","msg":"身材高挑的韓國25歲內衣女模Jisoo，因為與人氣女團BLACK PINK成員Jisoo撞名而惹起關注，進軍模界不足兩年，便已累積一定知名度，不時透過社交網分享靚相吸Like！<br />\n<br />\n形象高貴的Jisoo展現與實際年齡不一樣的成熟美，難怪深受首飾品牌的青睞，邀她拍攝廣告。而向來喜愛旅行的她，甚懂享受生活，之前曾到過日本、泰國、關島及濟州島歎世界，除了品嘗各地美食，亦喜愛喝紅酒，以及享受陽光與海灘。身材索爆的Jisoo又會特地到下榻酒店拍攝泳衣照。雖然她經常在旅行期間狂擦美食，但在拍攝內衣寫真前一段日子，便會努力節食，務求以最弗狀態示人，而她最愛玩瑜伽瘦身。<br />\n<br />\nProfile：<br />\n年齡：25歲<br />\n身高：1米67<br />\n體重：46kg<br />\n三圍：34D、24、33"},{"pid":"1315745834c47ac280fbb1fdcd29330520eca73a","tid":2076243,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200623/photo/bkn-20200623120046838-0623_00862_001_02b.jpg?20200623120400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200623120046838-0623_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20200623120400&h=7ffb0831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200623/photo/bkn-20200623120046838-0623_00862_001_03b.jpg?20200623120400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200623120046838-0623_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20200623120400&h=fede6d16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1ef74c9b233a31fed33d6aff02e13a4d9158dfe","tid":2076243,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200623/photo/bkn-20200623120046838-0623_00862_001_04b.jpg?20200623120400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fb